How to request transfers (email):
Dear Customer,

Thank you for your response.

You can request transfers from other Paysend users.

To request the transfer please go to:

• Log in, or register, to the Paysend the app;
• On the Transfers home page, push the Request button;
• Enter the sender's phone number
• Enter the amount you request;
• Select the card you want to receive funds to or enter the details of a new card;
• Enter the purpose of the transfer (why do you request the funds);
• Click Request

The sender will get the notification and will be able to send you funds on the card you have chosen.

If you have any more questions or need further assistance, please do not hesitate to reach out to us. We will be more than happy to help you.

Thank you for your understanding.

